ygData.messageBody:
Iksar monks may have beter regan but Human monks
outdamage Iksar.<br>Human= more power less regan<br>Iksar =
less power more regan<br>Human monks start with duel
weild<br>With iksar if u ever want to travel places safely u we
need to do soooooooooooooo much faction work. Its a
waste of time Human monk is just as good as iksar. And
just the fact when kunark came out everyone had a
twink iksar monk running around. <br><br>As for necro
vs sk . Necro will not win every fight. If the sk
has his resist gear on its going to be very hard for
the necro to get spells to land. And if the necro can
not get dark on and the sk is close necro = dead
quick. And the sk pet is just to keep the necro pet off
the sk for a lil bit. Any class can beat anyother
class on any given day.
